{"id":102296,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":7,"day":8}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"文化街","genre":"","count":"93","ytitle":"","mtitle":"荒田","ftitle":"","authors":["冯伊湄"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯伊湄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广西全州民众，抗敌最烈，故焚烧亦最惨。三十五年春过之，荒田万顷，饿殍载道，唯杜鹃花如火，满绣荒山耳。"}]}